OL,3,CDoctor had 'never seen' ME patient
OL,4,Cwith such severe symptoms, inquest told
OL,6,FHowever, Dr Fox said he was concerned
OL,7,Fabout her condition deteriorating.
OL,9,FIn March 2021, he said the hospital
OL,10,Fwas coming out of a wave of Covid,
OL,11,Fvaccinations were still not
OL,12,Fwidespread, and the risk of infection
OL,13,Fspreading was extremely high.
OL,15,FDr Fox agreed that Maeve's discharge
OL,16,Fnotes said she was keen to be sent
OL,17,Fhome.
OL,19,FLike all doctors giving evidence at
OL,20,Fthe inquest, he was asked about his
OL,21,Fknowledge of ME.
